job_history.work_description: Performing line maintenance functions, troubleshooting functions on electrical, hydraulic, engine and airframe systems and components, performing heavy maintenance, and maintaining records of maintenance and repair.

Troubleshooting malfunctions, maintaining, inspecting, and repairing aircraft structures and hydraulic systems and components, and collaborating with supervisors or higher-level technicians on complex aircraft relevant tasks.

skills.name: Aircraft Maintenance
skills.explanation: Over a decade of experience in performing line maintenance, troubleshooting, and heavy maintenance functions, indicating expert-level mastery.

skills.name: Troubleshooting
skills.explanation: Consistently applied troubleshooting skills on various aircraft systems and components, suggesting strong proficiency.

skills.name: Hydraulic Systems
skills.explanation: Maintained, inspected, and repaired hydraulic systems and components, indicating strong proficiency.

skills.name: Electrical Systems
skills.explanation: Performed line maintenance functions on electrical systems, showing a solid working proficiency.

skills.name: Airframe Systems
skills.explanation: Maintained, inspected, and repaired airframe systems and components, indicating a solid working proficiency.

skills.name: Leadership
skills.explanation: Collaborated with supervisors or higher-level technicians on complex tasks, suggesting some practical experience in leadership.

skills.name: Record Keeping
skills.explanation: Maintained records of maintenance and repair, showing a solid working proficiency.
